title: Friday Football Feast in Lakeville!
description: PA and Charch are live out at the Buffalo Wild Wings in Lakeville for the final regular season Friday Football Feast! Wobby and Chad Greenway join the show as per usual and Bears guy LaVelle E. Neal III is forced to talk about his team!
